Use Case: MoveShip
Scope: BattleShip
Primary Actor: User
Intention: Move a ship from one location on the gamemap
           to a new location desired by the User.
Level: Subfunction
Multiplicity: The User can only move a ship once per
              turn per game.
Main Success Scenario:
  1. User tells System his selection of ship by clicking it.
  2. System highlights the selected ship and accessible points
     surrounding the ship.
  3. User selects a new location for the ship and informs the System
  4. System verifies the new location is valid
  5. System moves the ship to the new location and shows the User.
     Use Case ends in success.
Extensions:
  1-3a. User informs the System he would like to perform a different action.
        Use Case ends in success.
  3a. User informs the System he would like to move a different ship.
      Use Case continues at step 1.
  4a. System informs the User that the new location is invalid.
     Use case continues at step 3.
